  "id": "api/forms/EmailValidator",
  "title": "EmailValidator",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/EmailValidator\", \"name\": \"EmailValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L563-L628\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L563-L628\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"emailvalidator\">EmailValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#emailvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A directive that adds the <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> validator to controls marked with the\n<code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n<p>该指令会借助 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 绑定把 <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> 验证器添加到任何带有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> 属性的控件上。</p>\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表单验证</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"email\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></span>: boolean | string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p>Tracks changes to the email attribute bound to this directive.</p>\n<p>跟踪绑定到该指令的 email 属性的更改。</p></div>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p>The email validation is based on the WHATWG HTML specification with some enhancements to\nincorporate more RFC rules. More information can be found on the <a href=\"api/forms/Validators#email\">Validators.email\npage</a>.</p>\n<p>电子邮件验证基于 WHATWG HTML 规范，并进行了一些增强以包含更多 RFC\n规则。更多信息，请参阅<a href=\"api/forms/Validators#email\">Validator.email 页面</a>。</p>\n\n    <h3 id=\"adding-an-email-validator\">Adding an email validator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#adding-an-email-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<h3 id=\"添加-email-验证器\">添加 email 验证器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#添加-email-验证器\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p>The following example shows how to add an email validator to an input attached to an ngModel*\nbinding.</p>\n<p>下面的例子演示了如何为一个带有 ngModel 绑定的输入框添加 email 验证器。</p>\n<code-example>\n&#x3C;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>>\n&#x3C;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>=\"true\">\n&#x3C;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> [<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>]=\"true\">\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validators\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/typed-forms\n - guide/update-to-version-14\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#adding-an-email-validator\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#description\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#emailvalidator\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#instance-properties\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#导出自\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#添加-email-验证器\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validators#email\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L563-L628\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L563-L628\n-->"
}